{"build_type":"library","module_name":"reap-completed-worker-slots-across-block-ring","package_name":"reap-completed-worker-slots-across-block-ring","description":"Design 4.4b: collector-driven as-completed reaper entry. Reads the block-ring (state[10]) and spawn cursor head (state[7]) and reaps every completed worker's {prctx, block, stack, chunks} back into the reaper's thread-local g_arena_free_list via reap-ring-slots-iteration. blocking=0 (per-wake, peek-and-skip live workers); blocking=1 (end-of-stream sweep, waits stragglers mid-exit). Keeps the pool footprint at the concurrent working set instead of the whole tree.","function_definitions":{"reap-completed-worker-slots-across-block-ring":{"return_type":"i64","parameter_definitions":[{"parameter_name":"state","parameter_type":"i64"},{"parameter_name":"blocking","parameter_type":"i64"}],"execution_instructions":[{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"zero","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":0},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"ten","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":10},{"instruction_type":"variable_declaration","variable_name":"seven","variable_type":"i64","assignment_operation":"literal","source_target":7},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"block_ring","base":"state","index":"ten","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"array_read","dest":"head","base":"state","index":"seven","scale":8},{"instruction_type":"function_invocation","invocation_name":"reap-ring-slots-iteration","invocation_arguments":[{"kind":"var","value":"block_ring"},{"kind":"var","value":"zero"},{"kind":"var","value":"head"},{"kind":"var","value":"blocking"}],"result_assignment_variable":"r","result_type":"i64"},{"instruction_type":"return_statement","return_payload":{"value":"r"}}]}}}